class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="gould-barbers" class="entry-website-title">Gould Barbers</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-gould-barbers-3840x12926-20240627.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-gould-barbers-3840x12926-20240627.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-gould-barbers-3840x12926-20240627.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Gould Barbers"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://www.gouldbarbers.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://www.gouldbarbers.co.uk/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>England, U.K.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Gould Barbers is a family-owned barbershop that offers a traditional barbering experience. The website has a powerful look with a dark color scheme and a good selection of high-quality images that capture the barbershop's classic appeal. The site features page links to the company's history and contact options, as well as a dedicated section on its grooming services.</p><p>The site's "Barbershop Finder" tool helps visitors easily find their nearest salon and book an appointment online. The prompt to "START YOUR CAREER" on the home page will appeal to aspiring barbers in search of an apprentice program.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The company offers specialist services for children, as well as discounted rates for seniors, which encourages a wide variety of clients to visit the barbershop. According to WAVE, the website has no contrast errors, indicating optimal readability.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The website would benefit from dedicated client reviews or testimonials for increased credibility, as well as pricing information to give users a more comprehensive overview of the barbershop's services.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-gould-barbers-3840x12926-20240627.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-gould-barbers-3840x12926-20240627.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website effectively advertises the barbershop with refined images and content sections expanding on its various locations and services. However, the site is missing a sticky top menu bar and back-to-top button, which slightly hinders navigation. Performance-wise, Google's PageSpeed Insights test indicates fast page loading times and an optimal performance score of 100/100.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-gould-barbers-824x10959-20240627.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-gould-barbers-824x10959-20240627.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>While all content and images slim down nicely on the mobile version without losing functionality, the "Find a Barbershop" CTA button gets hidden behind the hamburger menu and loses its prominence on mobile. The site's body text should also be enlarged slightly for easier readability. According to Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the website scored 74/100 in the performance category.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="imperium-barbershop" class="entry-website-title">Imperium Barbershop</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-imperium-barbershop-3840x16364-20240628.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-imperium-barbershop-3840x16364-20240628.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-imperium-barbershop-3840x16364-20240628.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Imperium Barbershop"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://www.imperiumbarber.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://www.imperiumbarber.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Toronto, Ontario, Canada</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Imperium Barbershop is a Toronto-based provider of hair and beard grooming services. The website effectively captures the company's luxurious appeal with a powerful color scheme and high-resolution images showcasing its services and workspace.</p><p>While the home page's hero video does not depict anything in particular, there is a video on the "About" page that introduces the barbershop to customers in an engaging manner. Visitors can also easily access the site's page links to learn more about the company's stylists, as well as its location and contact options.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site's online booking system allows users to quickly and easily organize their next haircut with the barbershop. The addition of a comprehensive style gallery also gives potential clients a good overview of the company's offerings.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>WAVE picked up several instances of insufficient contrast ratios throughout the website. The site would also benefit from additional resources, such as pricing guides, to ensure users have easy access to vital information.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-imperium-barbershop-3840x16364-20240628.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-imperium-barbershop-3840x16364-20240628.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop version has a professional appearance and the use of ample white space ensures all content is easily readable across the site. While site navigation is intuitive, several pages are quite slow to load and should be optimized for a better user experience. The website's performance score, however, is decent at 70/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-imperium-barbershop-824x16312-20240627.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-imperium-barbershop-824x16312-20240627.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>Like the desktop site, the mobile version performs well and retains its visual appeal with high-quality images breaking up some of the text-heavy sections. However, the hamburger menu's transparent background creates an insufficient contrast ratio and makes it difficult to read the page links and the "Booking" CTA button. On Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the site has a performance score of 45/100.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
