class="entry-text"><p>The desktop version's minimalistic page layouts allow the images and content to shine, specifically on the "Services" and "Contact" pages. However, upsizing some of the content will ensure optimal readability and the inclusion of additional CTA buttons in the top menu bar would be beneficial for increased user engagement. On Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the site scored 65/100 in the performance category.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
